body:
### Welcome to one of the coolest boilerplates in C#. NET.
There is not any specific rhyme or reason (scope) for this VS Project.  

### Designer Templates
If you want to test or link to this project to save steps or set in motion some architectural concepts in a hurry please take time to evaluate the comments and code first before submitting support questions. 

### Authors and Contributors
